scene.message:
Ayase: That can't be!{nl}
We all worked so hard to{nl}
gather them - the "Mirror{waitkey}Shards"!{waitkey}{clearbox}H-hey, let's hold it{nl}
up once more!{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen's Voice: Hffff...{nl}
It's useless. Thrusting a{nl}
patchwork mirror like that{waitkey}at me - you lose.{waitkey}{ret}

Snow Queen: Hffff...{waitkey}{nl}
Gathering the shards was{nl}
well done, but it seems{waitkey}you were a few short.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, come to me!{waitkey}{clearbox}Taste an endless nightmare,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
the despair of a dark night,{wait_fr:30}{nl}
together with Saeko!!{waitkey}{ret}

???: Cuuurse yooou{waitkey}{nl}
whyyy{waitkey}{clearbox}whyyy{wait_fr:30}{nl}
everyooone{wait_fr:30} Saekooo{wait_fr:30}{nl}
all of yoooou{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: You've all grown{nl}
so much in this short time.{waitkey}{clearbox}You've got the faces of{nl}
people who can do anything.{waitkey}{clearbox}As you are now, I feel like{nl}
you can pull something off.{waitkey}{clearbox}Sever the karma of the mask{nl}
that tormented so many{nl}
students! I'm counting on you.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: The Night Queen...{nl}
{waitkey}{clearbox}That thing said something{nl}
like "I'll rain snow of{nl}
despair from the{nl}
castle's peak."{waitkey}{clearbox}There may be a passage or{nl}
something the Queen climbed{nl}
up. Let's go look!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Just a little more...{nl}
A little more and the{nl}
school's ours again.{waitkey}Let's set out anew!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Don't you feel like{nl}
it got a little warmer?{nl}
Maybe the Queen's power{nl}
weakened?{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh yeah!!{waitkey}{nl}
Maybe the doors that were{nl}
frozen shut are fixed now!?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, let's hurry up{nl}
to the upper floor.{waitkey}{clearbox}If my tummy gets cold before{nl}
we beat the Queen, I won't{nl}
be in any state to fight!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It's been quite a{nl}
while since Inaba and{nl}
Sonomura went outside.{waitkey}{clearbox}We must settle this soon -{nl}
I'm worried about them.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The Night Queen~?{nl}
Like a Ginza bar madam.{nl}
Doesn't seem all that tough.{waitkey}{clearbox}You'd be fine without{nl}
me, right?{waitkey}{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}Just kidding.{nl}
C'mon, let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: To sever the mask's{nl}
karma, we must defeat the{nl}
Night Queen no matter what.{waitkey}{ret}
